I don't want to talk about it now.

136
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:21,598
Ohh.

137
00:06:21,666 --> 00:06:22,148
Just...

138
00:06:22,149 --> 00:06:25,040
Look, I know this is
a crappy day for you,

139
00:06:25,109 --> 00:06:27,065
