172
00:07:42,236 --> 00:07:45,171
Hey, Carlos. Uh, why don't you
take, uh, Maria and the kids

173
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:48,141
Inside and introduce them to the girls?
- Come on, guys.

174
00:07:48,210 --> 00:07:49,997
Come on in.
- All right. Let's go.

175
00:07:52,665 --> 00:07:55,229
